Global Pistol Electric Screwdriver Market Insights
Pistol Electric Screwdriver Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Pistol Electric Screwdriver Market Overview
The global market for Pistol Electric Screwdrivers was valued at approximately USD 2.5 billion in 2024, with a projected compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.1% from 2025 to 2030. This robust growth is attributed to the increasing demand for efficient power tools across industries such as automotive, construction, and electronics. The market is expected to witness substantial growth due to the growing preference for automated tools in DIY and professional applications. Additionally, the rising adoption of cordless electric screwdrivers and advancements in battery technology are expected to drive further demand in the coming years.

